Title: crosshyb
Description: Character vector of Illumina probes whose probe sequence promiscuously aligns to non-target sections of the genome matching 47bp or higher.

Title: snpsall
Description: Data.frame of Illumina probes whose target CpG lies on or near a known SNP. SNP ID, distance to CpG and minor allele frequency are all reported here.

Title: XY.probes
Description: Character vector of Illumina probes whose target CpG site is on a sex chromosome.

Title: hg19.generanges
Description: GRanges object giving the genomic intervals of all gene regions in the Ensembl Release 75 of hg19.

Title: hg38.generanges
Description: GRanges object giving the genomic intervals of all gene regions in the Ensembl Release 96 of hg38.

Title: mm10.generanges
Description: GRanges object giving the genomic intervals of all gene regions in the Ensembl Release 96 of mm10.
